Citation.sTitle: Densities and Viscosities of Binary Mixtures of Tris(2-ethylhexyl) Phosphate + Cyclohexane or n-Hexane at T ) (293.15, 298.15, and 303.15) K and p ) 0.1 MPa
Citation.sAbstract: This work presents densities and viscosities under atmospheric conditions for tris(2-ethylhexyl) phosphate with cyclohexane and n-hexane over the whole range of composition at T ) (293.15, 298.15, and 303.15) K. The viscosity data have been represented by the EyringsUNIQUAC equation for liquid mixture viscosity.
